DISCIPLINARY DOCKET

97-2273. Cleveland Bar Assn. v. Belock.

On December 26, 1997, respondent filed a reply brief to respondent’s answer brief. Whereas Gov.Bar R. V does not provide for the filing of a reply brief,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that the reply brief be, and hereby is, stricken.
